{
  "script_id": "jacobian",
  "voice": "zh-CN-YunxiNeural",
  "voice_key": "yunxi",
  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "jacobian",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/jacobian/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.48,
      "size": 39744,
      "text": "一个平面映射，能把整齐的方格网弯成螺旋、扇形或波浪。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "jacobian",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/jacobian/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.77,
      "size": 28368,
      "text": "整体看它是弯曲的，可如果只盯着一个小方块呢？"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "jacobian",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/jacobian/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.95,
      "size": 31248,
      "text": "放大再放大，那一小块几乎变回了平行四边形。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "jacobian",
      "section_id": "local",
      "line_id": "def-1",
      "filename": "local-def-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/jacobian/local-def-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.16,
      "size": 34560,
      "text": "这就是微积分的核心思想：弯曲的东西，局部看都是线性的。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "jacobian",
      "section_id": "local",
      "line_id": "def-2",
      "filename": "local-def-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/jacobian/local-def-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.74,
      "size": 27792,
      "text": "在某一点附近，映射近似成一次的拉伸加旋转。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "jacobian",
      "section_id": "local",
      "line_id": "def-3",
      "filename": "local-def-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/jacobian/local-def-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.63,
      "size": 26064,
      "text": "描述这份局部线性的，正是雅可比矩阵。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "jacobian",
      "section_id": "matrix",
      "line_id": "mat-1",
      "filename": "matrix-mat-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/jacobian/matrix-mat-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.31,
      "size": 37008,
      "text": "把 x、y 分别对 u、v 求偏导，排成一个二乘二的矩阵。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "jacobian",
      "section_id": "matrix",
      "line_id": "mat-2",
      "filename": "matrix-mat-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/jacobian/matrix-mat-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.25,
      "size": 36000,
      "text": "每一列告诉你，沿 u 或沿 v 走一步，像点朝哪个方向移动多远。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "jacobian",
      "section_id": "matrix",
      "line_id": "mat-3",
      "filename": "matrix-mat-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/jacobian/matrix-mat-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.92,
      "size": 30672,
      "text": "这里我们用数值差分算偏导，对任何映射都通用。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "jacobian",
      "section_id": "det",
      "line_id": "det-1",
      "filename": "det-det-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/jacobian/det-det-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.8,
      "size": 28800,
      "text": "雅可比矩阵的行列式，就是局部面积的缩放因子。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "jacobian",
      "section_id": "det",
      "line_id": "det-2",
      "filename": "det-det-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/jacobian/det-det-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.18,
      "size": 34848,
      "text": "行列式大于一，小方块被放大；小于一，则被压缩。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "jacobian",
      "section_id": "det",
      "line_id": "det-3",
      "filename": "det-det-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/jacobian/det-det-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.47,
      "size": 39456,
      "text": "换元积分里的 dxdy 等于 |det J| 乘 dudv，来源就在这里。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "jacobian",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/jacobian/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.85,
      "size": 29664,
      "text": "移动高亮的方块，看它在不同位置被拉伸的程度。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "jacobian",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/jacobian/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.67,
      "size": 26640,
      "text": "换一个映射，观察面积比如何随位置改变。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "jacobian",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/jacobian/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.21,
      "size": 35424,
      "text": "雅可比矩阵把弯曲映射的局部行为，压缩成一个线性变换。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "jacobian",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/jacobian/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.89,
      "size": 30240,
      "text": "它的行列式衡量面积的缩放，是换元积分的钥匙。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "jacobian",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-3",
      "filename": "summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/jacobian/summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.01,
      "size": 32112,
      "text": "弯曲之中藏着线性，这就是微积分的魔法，我们下次再见！"
    }
  ],
